  "text": "There are few studies, which evaluated the relation between clinicopathologic aspects of tumor and the presence of hepatic micrometastasis. In Yokoyama et al. study some of these variables such as gender, age, location of tumor and Duke stage have been evaluated. [CITATION_1] In line with our results, they also revealed that none of these variables had a signifi cant relation with the presence of micrometastasis.",
